  h2.title About the Journal
  p.base-text International Journal of Creative Research and Publications (IJCRP) is an international, peer-reviewed, multidisciplinary research journal committed to the dissemination of high-quality original research, review papers, case studies, and scholarly articles across diverse academic disciplines. The journal serves as a global platform for researchers, academicians, professionals, and scholars to share innovative ideas, critical insights, and creative research outcomes.
    br
    | IJCRP aims to promote intellectual exchange and interdisciplinary dialogue by publishing research that addresses contemporary issues, emerging trends, and real-world challenges. The journal encourages original contributions that advance knowledge, integrate theory with practice, and contribute meaningfully to academic and professional communities worldwide.
    br
    | Published exclusively in online mode, IJCRP ensures rapid dissemination, global accessibility, and academic visibility while maintaining strict ethical standards and a rigorous double-blind peer-review process to uphold research integrity and publication quality.

