  h3.title Aim and Scope
  p.base-text The International Journal of Creative Research and Publications (IJCRP) is dedicated to advancing scholarly knowledge and promoting multidisciplinary research across a wide spectrum of academic disciplines. The journal provides an inclusive platform for creative, analytical, and empirical research that contributes to theoretical development, practical applications, and societal advancement.

  h2.title Areas Covered (but not limited to):

  h4.title Social Sciences, Arts & Humanities
  p.base-text Anthropology, Archaeology, History, Geography, Geology, Law, Political Science, Governance, Public Administration, Philosophy, Sociology, Civics, Demography, Economics, Journalism, Media Studies, Performing Arts, Visual Arts, Fine Arts, Culture Studies, Development Studies.

  h4.title Education & Allied Studies
  p.base-text Education, Special Education, Physical Education, Teacher Education, Linguistics, Literature, Language Studies, Yogic Studies, Sports Studies, Rehabilitation Studies, Home Science.

  h4.title Management & Commerce
  p.base-text Business Administration, Management Studies, Commerce, Finance, Accounting, Economics, Human Resource Management, Marketing, Sales, Operations Management, Information Management, Organisational Behaviour, Organisational Strategy, Business Law, Entrepreneurship, Hospitality and Hotel Management.

  h4.title Science
  p.base-text Logic, Mathematics, Statistics, Physics, Chemistry, Biology, Earth Science, Environmental Science, Soil Science, Plant Science, Ecology, Space Science, Biochemistry, Microbiology, Biotechnology, Life Sciences, Astronomy, Zoology, Entomology, Agriculture, Dairy Science.

  h4.title Engineering & Technology
  p.base-text Civil Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, Electrical Engineering, Electronics Engineering, Computer Science, Information Technology, Artificial Intelligence, Data Science, Emerging Technologies.

  h4.title Health & Medical Sciences
  p.base-text Hospital Administration, Nutrition, Medicine, Pharmacy, Pharmaceutics, AYUSH (Ayurveda, Unani, Siddha, Homeopathy), Forensic Medicine, Dermatology, Orthopedics, Dentistry, Oral Surgery, Obstetrics and Gynecology, Pediatrics, Oncology, Radiology, Clinical Medicine, Tropical Medicine, Parasitology, Infectious Diseases, Biomedical Sciences, Medical Biotechnology, Immunology, Diagnostics Imaging, Cardiology, Toxicology, Veterinary Science, Animal Husbandry.

  h4.title Languages
  p.base-text All Indian and Foreign Languages


  h3.title Editorial Board:
  p.base-text We are confident that the expertise, academic excellence, and professional guidance of our Editorial Board will significantly contribute to the continued success and scholarly impact of IJCRP. The Editorial Board comprises experienced academicians, researchers, and subject experts from diverse disciplines who ensure the maintenance of high academic standards, ethical publishing practices, and the publication of quality research. Their active involvement strengthens the journal's commitment to publishing research that addresses contemporary challenges and drives progress in both theory and practice. (
    a(href="#", class="text-blue-500 hover:underline") Click Here 
    |)


  h3.title Submission Guidelines:
  p.base-text Authors are invited to submit original, unpublished manuscripts that are not under consideration elsewhere. For manuscript submission procedures, formatting requirements, ethical policies, and further details, authors are requested to visit the (
    a(href="#", class="text-blue-500 hover:underline") Author Instructions
    |) page available on the journal's website. Detailed submission guidelines and manuscript preparation instructions are provided to ensure transparency, uniformity, and smooth processing of submissions.(
    a(href="#", class="text-blue-500 hover:underline") Author Instructions
    |)


  h3.title Readership:
  p.base-text IJCRP caters to a wide readership, including researchers, academicians, scholars, students, policymakers, industry professionals, and practitioners across multiple disciplines. We highly value the contributions of our readership and remain committed to delivering impactful, relevant, and high-quality scholarly content that fosters academic growth, innovation, and interdisciplinary understanding.

